00:00:16.683 --> 00:00:17.809 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO]
Yo.

00:00:17.892 --> 00:00:18.977 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry for making you
stick your neck out

00:00:19.060 --> 00:00:20.937 position:50% align:center
for me like this, Rei.

00:00:21.021 --> 00:00:22.772 position:50% align:center
What's up?

00:00:22.856 --> 00:00:25.692 position:50% align:center
